    "Similarly, if text-based DocIDs fail to precisely represent the documents, the model also tend to rote learning.A potential solution is to create a large-scale pre-training dataset for generative retrieval on a general corpus, possibly including a variety of common DocIDs such as URLs, titles, and numerical sequences.",
